data.description: **"Welcome to this magnificent 4-bedroom, 3,268 sq ft home in beautiful Delta County! Remodeled in 2010, this spacious property boasts an open kitchen with granite countertops, a gas range, and double wall ovens. Additional features include a dedicated crafting room, a second living space, and a furnace room.The 1.56-acre lot is perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and comes with irrigation water for added convenience.  But that's not all! The property includes a large, wired and plumbed for gas for a heated shop that's a dream come true for hobbyists. Inside the shop, you'll find a concrete pit with electricity, making it ideal for all your projects.   With its picturesque views and ample space both inside and out, this property offers the ultimate in comfort and functionality. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours – contact us today for more details or to schedule a viewing!"**
